    <title>Arctic contributor: Peter Varga</title>
    <description>Peter Varga has plied his trade as a journalist in the Canadian Arctic and Quebec for a variety of print outlets, most recently for the Montreal Gazette and Nunatsiaq News in Iqaluit, Nunavut. He has written and photographed, edited and reported for magazine, newspaper and online publications in Greater Montreal, Nunavut, Northwest Territories, Quebec’s Eastern Townships and Vermont.
</description>
